        "heading": "<h2>Employment Opportunities</h2>",
        "richtext": "<p>We are always looking to connect with talented, high-character individuals who align with our values. If you are excited about our products and our approach and interested in employment with Simple Modern, please send an introduction email and resume to jobs@simplemodern.com. We strive to acknowledge each email received, but please note that due to the high volume of interest, an immediate response may not be feasible. We look forward to connecting with you!</p>"
